</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_145" id="72r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_145_line_1576580464891_3926"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft cʒü <expan>VVermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l3">vicʒtüm in Nydern Beyrn / . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_145_r2l4">Lıeber her Vicʒtüm / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>püchſe<ex>n</ex>meiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l5">Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> mit Jm geredt / vnd er ſprıchet / daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Jm </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l6">
<del rend="strikethrough">d </del> er des nicht tun wöll / wan er vor <expan>etlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> püchſen <expan>gegoʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l7">hab / die Jm den lon noch ſchuldig <expan>beleıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / darvmb 
<del rend="strikethrough"> d </del> er das verredt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l8">hab / vnd <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mer <expan>gieſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöll / vnd main 
<del rend="strikethrough"> glo </del> ſich ſüſt mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l9">glocken gieſſen vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> arbeit wol cʒü erneren / . Alſo daʒ vvir Jn des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l10">nicht v̈berreden künnen / So <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteet</expan> Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_145_line_1584551796766_353"><expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> wol / daʒ vns nicht füglıch <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l11">daʒ vvir Jn des <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> ſeinen willen nötten <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / wo vvir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l12">erberkeit ſüſt lıeb vnd dienſt beweiſen <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l14"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Marie <expan>Mag<ex>dale</ex><hi rend="sup">ne</hi></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_145" id="72r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft czü
                            <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, vicztüm in Nydern Beyrn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her vicztüm, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        habt umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>püchse<ex>n</ex>meist<ex>er</ex></expan>, also
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> mit im geredt und er sprichet, daz er des
                        nicht tun wöll, wan er vor <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> püchsen <expan>gegozze<ex>n</ex></expan> hab,
                        die im den lon noch schuldig <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darumb er das
                        verredt hab und <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mer <expan>giesze<ex>n</ex></expan> wöll; und
                        main sich süst mit glocken giessen und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> arbeit
                        wol czü erneren. Also daz wir in des nicht überreden künnen, so
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steet</expan> ir
                                <add><expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan></add> wol, daz uns nicht füglich
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz wir in des
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> seinen willen nötten
                            <expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Wo wir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit süst lieb und dienst beweisen
                                <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Marie
                                <expan>Mag<ex>dale</ex><hi rend="sup">ne</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
